APUS: fast and scalable paxos on RDMA
=====================================

Build APUS
----------
The code base of APUS is based on DARE [HPDC'15]

Prerequisites
 - libev
 - libconfig
 - libdb
 - libibverbs

0. Commands to checkout a brand-new project:
 > git clone https://github.com/hku-systems/apus
 > cd $PAXOS_ROOT
 
1. Set env vars in ~/.bashrc.
 > export PAXOS_ROOT=<absolute path of RDMA-PAXOS>

2. Compile.
 > cd target
 > make clean; make

Run examples
------------
0. Install Redis
 > cd apps/redis
 > ./mk

1. Run APUS with Redis
 > cd benchmarks
 > ./run.sh --app=redis

